(6. DESIGN RATIONALE) show newline
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) show newline
() show newline
(The Wilderness serves multiple purposes:) show newline
() show newline
(1. Honest onboarding - Users know they are not yet part of anything 2.) show newline
(Unified metaphor - Same space for unaffiliated and wormhole transit 3.) show newline
(Security clarity - No implicit trust, no assumed identity 4. Poetic) show newline
(resonance - Evokes the uncertainty of the unaffiliated state) show newline
